public enum ESyntacticCategory
extends java.lang.Enum<ESyntacticCategory>

Enumeration of the different categories of a SyntacticArgument instance.
A syntactic category is a set of words and/or phrases in a language which share a significant number of common characteristics.

Author:
Zijad Maksuti
